  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Social &amp; Behaviour Change Communication Campaign</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The &#x2018;Social and Behavioural Change Communication Campaign to Address COVID-19&#x2019; in Sierra Leone implemented by FOCUS 1000 aims to ensure that the general public, especially the most vulnerable &#x2013;the aged,  women, adolescent girls, young persons, families and communities - have the information, understanding and basic skills needed to address the health, SGBV or other challenges posed by the coronavirus situation. The objective is to mount an intensive evidenced-informed communication campaign that empowers the public with knowledge on recommended healthy and social protection behaviours regarding COVID-19 across the country. The key activities include conducting a series of KAP studies, carryout intensive campaigns and engage extensively with the Kombra Network.</narrative>
  </description>
